<p>
    I'm Nico, a software engineer from the Midwest! My interests in tech span performance engineering, parallelism, and low-level systems. I <a href="/writing">write</a> about computing, history, and philosophy. I also like to draw, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/155270767-nico" target="_blank">read books</a>, and recently started climbing. You can find me on <a href="https://github.com/nicosalm" target="_blank">GitHub</a> or say hi via <a href="#" data-email="ved.mlas@ocin">email [<span class="copy-label">copy</span>]</a>.</div>
</p>


